# WhatsApp Booking Bot SaaS

## Setup
1. Install Node.js
2. Run: npm install
3. Fill .env
4. Start: npm start

## Add client
POST /setup
{
 "name": "Business",
 "prices": "Haircut R100",
 "sheetId": "GOOGLE_SHEET_ID"
}

## Railway Deploy
- Create project
- Add env vars
- Deploy

## WhatsApp QR
- First run shows QR in console
- Scan with WhatsApp

## Google Sheets
- Enable API
- Create service account
- Share sheet with email
